<!--DO NOT REMOVE COMMENTS OR CHANGE FORMAT, EVERYTHING MUST STAY THE SAME FOR ANY SORT OF MODIFICATION-->
<!--This is a commented version of the physicstasks.ymt file for RDR2. Many things are still undiscovered. Other things are self explaining.-->
<!--Use this file for tests or to create your own euphoria mod-->
